    	  <div style="margin:0; padding:0 0 10px 8.3%; display:block;">Dear Colleague</div>
      
    <div style="margin:0; padding:0 10px 10px 8.3%; display:block;">I wanted to let you know that we have released an upgrade for Tense Buster. This will enable your students to run the program on an iPad or Android tablet. Due to size constraints, it will not run on phones.</div>
    
   
    
    <div style="margin:0; padding:0 10px 10px 8.3%; display:block;">As you currently subscribe to Tense Buster, you can switch to the new version immediately. But since this might not be a convenient time, we can also offer you a delayed switch on request.</div>
    
   
    
    <div style="margin:0; padding:0 0 5px 8.3%; display:block;"><strong>What happens if you switch now?</strong></div>
    <div style="margin:0; padding:0 10px 10px 8.3%; display:block;">This is a technical upgrade, so with a very few exceptions, the learning content is the same as V9.</div>
    <div style="margin:0; padding:0 10px 10px 8.3%; display:block;">If your students log in through <a href="http://www.clarityenglish.com" target="_blank">www.ClarityEnglish.com</a> they will simply go into the new version. Their name and password don't change. Progress records from the old version will be shown to students from within the new version and in Results Manager.</div>
    
    <div style="margin:0; padding:0 0 10px 8.3%; display:block;">If you use a direct URL to link to Tense Buster, this will not change. When the switch is made, we will send an email confirming all the details.</div>
    
    <div style="margin:0; padding:0 0 5px 8.3%; display:block;"><strong>When can I delay switching to?</strong></div>
    <div style="margin:0; padding:0 0 10px 8.3%; display:block;">We will offer both versions until 20th August 2014, at which point we will switch everyone. (If you have a very strong need to go past this date, do let us know.)</div>
    
     <div style="margin:0; padding:0 0 5px 8.3%; display:block;"><strong>Is there any cost?</strong></div>
    <div style="margin:0; padding:0 0 10px 8.3%; display:block;">No, we are providing the upgrade free of charge.</div>
    
    <div style="margin:0; padding:0 0 5px 8.3%; display:block;"><strong>What do I have to do now?</strong></div>
    <div style="margin:0; padding:0 0 10px 8.3%; display:block;">If you would like to keep the old version until 20th August 2014 just send a reply to this email. If we don't hear from you we will assume that you want to switch to the new version and we will do it in August 2014.</div>
    
    <div style="margin:0; padding:0 0 10px 8.3%; display:block;">If you have any questions about this, either now or after the switch, please let me know. I hope that you and your students enjoy the brand new Tense Buster V10.</div>    </td>
